					  SCAGA Cancels Legends Bramble  

					 by Jeffrey Barbas  |  June 18, 2010    No Comments  

					 

 The Stark County Amateur Golf Association has decided to cancel its June 27th “bramble” tournament at the Legends of Massillon Golf Club due to low registrations.  
 SCAGA’s next event will be The Stark County Amateur, to be played at Prestwick, Seven Hills and The Sanctuary on July 23-25th. To enter, visit the  SCAGA website . 

					 

					   

			

					
			

